desc: I HAVE BEEN IN THE RETAIL BUSINESS FOR MOST OF MY ADULT LIFE... I AM BLESSED TO LIVE IN MALIBU OVERLOOKING THE PACIFIC OCEAN AND I USE MY DAILY INSPIRATIONS TO GUIDE ME WITH MY CREATIONS. MANY OF MY DESIGNS CAN BE SEEN ON MANY LOCAL MALIBU CELEBRITIES! HAVE FUN SHOPPING AND REMEMBER TO SMILE!!!

layout.text: JEWELERY INSPIRED BY NATURE & THE MALIBU LIFESTYLE
From fun jewelery to fine jewelery there is something for everyone.
